{"tid":1886534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"違規冇王管 營友促警駐守","createTime":"2020-02-19T03:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T07:13:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"71d07ec133cb37906541f7e59a55aee215eb38a4","tid":1886534,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:09:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200219/4DTMRDA2XBWFTFZDEW4MRZGF7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200219%2F4DTMRDA2XBWFTFZDEW4MRZGF7A%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=ec2a52dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200219%2F4DTMRDA2XBWFTFZDEW4MRZGF7A%2F&h=80b7f26d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200219/4DTMRDA2XBWFTFZDEW4MRZGF7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n違規冇王管 營友促警駐守<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200219/large/1582042614_62cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200219%2Flarge%2F1582042614_62cb.jpg&h=e7a61648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nK先生目擊有營友於隔離營內吸煙，部份人沒戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「自律係冇用！」曾入隔離營的K先生表示，短短數天已目擊營友多次違規，包括有人出外拒戴口罩、戶外吸煙冇王管，以及營友之間互相探訪並長時間逗留對方單位。他認為隔離營靠民安隊看守，欠執法權和阻嚇力，如改由警方駐守較令人安心。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：家具運抵駿洋邨 警重兵駐守<br />\n<br />\n無清潔用品 靠滾水消毒<br />\n<br />\nK先生和妻子月初入住麥理浩夫人度假村隔離九天。他形容隔離日子枯燥乏味，加上營地偏僻令手機訊號微弱，難以上網接收資訊，「好似去咗個荒島咁」，與世隔絕。他指有營友不甘寂寞，防疫意識鬆懈，頻頻到戶外除下口罩吸煙、集體聚集接收Wi-Fi訊號，又到其他住所探訪，更進入對方單位一起吃飯、聊天。他批評隔離措施形同虛設，令人擔心「究竟係隔離營定傳染營呢？自己諗」。<br />\n<br />\n入營守則訂明，隔離人士應盡量留在營舍內，要有需要暫時離開便要戴上口罩。但以K觀察，負責維持秩序的民安隊甚少派人巡邏，服務站亦只得兩名職員當值，他曾向民安隊投訴，但當值人員只口頭勸喻，如改為警員執法會令他感到安心。他又投訴，隔離營醫療人員欠衞生意識，有職員為他從耳朵探熱時，忘記更換透明膠耳套，質疑相關人士欠專業訓練。隔離期間，職員亦未有派發清潔用品，維持屋內衞生惟有「煲盆滾水」，定期清潔門柄和屋內設施。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署回覆指，檢疫中心會要求接受檢疫人士盡量留在營舍及指定範圍，如有需要暫時離開營舍須戴口罩；接受檢疫的人士應注意衞生，保持健康的生活模式和避免吸煙。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁銘恩"},{"pid":"8ff197a7a7651f020278470ebe5b965526a6a09b","tid":1886534,"uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"警察都無王管啦 笑"},{"pid":"c18016b297617af7cb1a3e2e4bc70099165247f5","tid":1886534,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ff197a7a7651f020278470ebe5b965526a6a09b","tid":1886534,"uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"警察都無王管啦 笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:11:58.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾陸期牆紙】 Failed State<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1886293/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1886293/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=29980f2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=edea0c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhongkong_wallpaper%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=2ebc1a15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/</a><br />\nWEB: <a href=\"https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffirsthand-news.web.app%2Fwallpaper%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=5c257c76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7F73j9S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7F73j9S.jpg&h=c80af059&s={SIZE}\"